WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:02.640
Didn't you get on the plane?

2
00:00:02.640 --> 00:00:05.660
Can I see such a good show if I leave?

3
00:00:06.040 --> 00:00:08.820
Director Gai, you have worked hard all these years

4
00:00:09.120 --> 00:00:10.540
Your name is Zhang Boran

5
00:00:10.640 --> 00:00:14.140
Yes I remember you were a nice young man

6
00:00:14.360 --> 00:00:15.360
How long has the internship been?

7
00:00:15.360 --> 00:00:16.240
Less than a month

8
00:00:16.240 --> 00:00:20.860
All right. You're officially hired next month.

9
00:00:21.080 --> 00:00:25.560
Isn't the internship period three months? We have a saying that Jingmen has an exception to hire

10
00:00:25.560 --> 00:00:27.180
There is no age limit.

11
00:00:27.880 --> 00:00:28.880
Thanks boss

12
00:00:28.880 --> 00:00:35.540
However, you must pass the bar examination within one year after you are officially hired

13
00:00:38.400 --> 00:00:42.260
This is what I just got yesterday, hahahaha.

14
00:00:42.320 --> 00:00:44.740
You really look good for the post-00 generation

15
00:00:44.840 --> 00:00:47.100
Take this thing away, but baby

16
00:00:47.600 --> 00:00:52.660
Let me ask you a question. Do you know why I hired Zhang Boran exceptionally?

17
00:00:53.400 --> 00:00:57.780
Why ask him why record you might think lawyers are just going to court

18
00:00:57.800 --> 00:00:58.680
Write a dossier

19
00:00:58.680 --> 00:01:01.800
Fight for the legitimate rights and interests of those who do not understand the law

20
00:01:01.800 --> 00:01:06.040
But in fact, lawyers should have chivalrous spirit in their bones

21
00:01:06.040 --> 00:01:08.740
It is the pride of breaking the world with the sword

22
00:01:08.920 --> 00:01:11.860
I saw this pride in Zhang Boran

23
00:01:12.040 --> 00:01:13.340
I'm not that great

24
00:01:13.440 --> 00:01:15.740
I'm doing this just for lawyer Tang Jian

25
00:01:17.520 --> 00:01:19.100
No matter who it is for

26
00:01:19.160 --> 00:01:21.640
Your spirit is right and commendable

27
00:01:21.640 --> 00:01:25.680
Director Pai, if you are willing to write me an inspection, I can consider it.

28
00:01:25.680 --> 00:01:26.960
Forget it

29
00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:28.940
I'll deliver it to you this afternoon.

